斗书写担当。\n传承东风精神\n1\n相信终有一天，我们会成为新时代的“铸剑人”，让东风精神代代相传，让祖国山河永远无恙！\n新时代的“铸剑人”\n2\n爱国情与报国行\n\n=== Slide 19 ===\n我的讲话完毕，谢谢大家！\n01\n讲话结束\n\n=== Slide 20 ===\n谢谢大家\n汇报人：AiPPT\n2025.10"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-ark-cn-beijing-volces-com","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":1381,"output":1089,"cacheRead":20280,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":22750,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774068175720}}
