{"type":"message","id":"df7c5e2f","parentId":"bf93db81","timestamp":"2026-03-21T04:46:31.956Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"现在我需要重构客户端调用部分，支持两种 API 格式。让我看看完整的生成函数：\n\n\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_lpusjjrs65blg5xb5rd3xv42","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace/skills/multimodal-quiz-generator/scripts/generate_quiz.py","limit":60,"offset":55}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-ark-cn-beijing-volces-com","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":776,"output":110,"cacheRead":25912,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":26798,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774068388005}}
{"type":"message","id":"adbe536f","parentId":"df7c5e2f","timestamp":"2026-03-21T04:46:31.967Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_lpusjjrs65blg5xb5rd3xv42","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"        if not key:\n            raise ValueError(\"Zhipu API key required. Set ZHIPU_API_KEY env var or use --api-key\")\n        return OpenAI(api_key=key, base_url=base_url or \"https://open.bigmodel.cn/api/paas/v4\")\n    \n    elif provider == 'ark':\n        key = api_key or os.environ.get('ARK_API_KEY')\n        if not key:\n            raise ValueError(\"Ark API key required. Set ARK_API_KEY env var or use --api-key\")\n        return OpenAI(api_key=key, base_url=base_url or \"https://ark.cn-beijing.volces.com/api/v3\")\n    \n    else:\n        raise ValueError(f\"Unknown provider: {provider}\")\n\ndef build_prompt(content, count, types):\n    \"\"\"Build prompt for LLM\"\"\"\n    type_names = [type_labels.get(t, t) for t in types]\n    type_str = \"、\".join(type_names)\n    \n    prompt = f\"\"\"请根据以下文档内容生成 {count} 道考试题目。\n\n## 文档内容\n{content}\n\n## 要求\n1. 题目类型包括：{type_str}\n2. 每道题必须包含：题目、答案、解析、难度\n3. 单选/多选/不定项题必须提供4个选项（A、B、C、D）\n4. 填空题用 __ 表示填空位置，并注明填空数和答案形式\n5. 解析必须说明答案在原文中的出处\n6. 难度分为：易、中、难\n7. 题目序号从1开始连续编号\n\n## 输出格式示例\n\n1.[单选]题目内容？\nA. 选项A\nB. 选项B\nC. 选项C\nD. 选项D\n答案：A\n解析：解析内容，说明在原文中的依据\n题目难度：中\n\n2.[多选]题目内容？\nA. 选项A\nB. 选项B\nC. 选项C\nD. 选项D\n答案：BCD\n解析：解析内容，说明在原文中的依据\n题目难度：中\n\n3.[不定项]题目内容？\nA. 选项A\nB. 选项B\nC. 选项C\nD. 选项D\n答案：BC\n解析：解析内容，说明在原文中的依据\n题目难度：中\n\n[123 more lines in file. Use offset=115 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774068391965}}
