{"type":"message","id":"cdcbb623","parentId":"1995c3f4","timestamp":"2026-03-21T04:48:05.338Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"明白了，baseUrl 是 `https://ark.cn-beijing.volces.com/api/coding`，我需要修正客户端的 baseUrl 拼接方式。Anthropic SDK 会自动处理路径：\n\n\n\n\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_tvs4252kpon2kf8rwzo6ao3n","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/Users/liuchenglong/.openclaw/workspace/skills/multimodal-quiz-generator/scripts/generate_quiz.py","old_string":"    elif provider == 'ark':\n        key = api_key or os.environ.get('ARK_API_KEY')\n        if not key:\n            raise ValueError(\"Ark API key required. Set ARK_API_KEY env var or use --api-key\")\n        # Volces Ark supports Anthropic-compatible messages API\n        client = anthropic.Anthropic(\n            api_key=key,\n            base_url=base_url or \"https://ark.cn-beijing.volces.com/api\"\n        )\n        return client, 'anthropic'","new_string":"    elif provider == 'ark':\n        key = api_key or os.environ.get('ARK_API_KEY')\n        if not key:\n            raise ValueError(\"Ark API key required. Set ARK_API_KEY env var or use --api-key\")\n        # Volces Ark supports Anthropic-compatible messages API\n        client = anthropic.Anthropic(\n            api_key=key,\n            base_url=base_url or \"https://ark.cn-beijing.volces.com/api/coding\"\n        )\n        return client, 'anthropic'"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"custom-ark-cn-beijing-volces-com","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":7893,"output":356,"cacheRead":22840,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":31089,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774068477140}}
